            "code_var_name": "domain_Omega",
            "description": "The main computational domain in which the physical problem is defined.\nJUSTIFICATION:\nThe domain of interest is defined as a region \u03a9 \u2282 R^d, and it is repeatedly referenced in integrals over the domain and its boundaries. This establishes it as the primary spatial domain of the problem.",
