            "code_var_name": "neumann_boundary_Gamma_t",
            "description": "The part of the boundary where Neumann boundary conditions (prescribed heat flux) are applied.\nJUSTIFICATION:\nThe boundary \u0393_t is explicitly defined as the region where Dirichlet and Neumann BCs are prescribed, respectively, and appears in the integral over the Neumann boundary.",
